GAME DESIGN

players start in human form
a player hit by an enemy dies
animal pajama appear after a certain number of points are collected
animal pajama grant super powers
players can loose their animal pajama when hit by enemies

 - frog pajama super power is throwing bubbles
 - fox pajama super power is throwing dynamite
 - pingoo pajama super power is freezing enemies

some terrain blocks are breakable by dynamite

killing all enemies in a level can unlock a revive item if one of the players is dead
killing all enemies in a level can unlock an animal pajama if one of the players is human

dead players can move around as ghosts but can do nothing
